hopobject.body: Go travelling cincotta discount pharmacy warrawong Nobody knows why Swartz did what he did. Given that he was an open-access activist, it's possible that he disapproved of JSTOR's paywall and wanted to make the fruits of academic research available to all. After he was arrested, he returned all of the downloaded copies to JSTOR, paid their legal expenses and JSTOR indicated that they would not be taking further legal action.
